.TH g-developer-db 1  "g-developer-db " 
.SH NAME
g\-developer\-db \- Open an interactive SQLite shell connected to the internal g.db database
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBg\-developer\-db\fR [\fB\-\-path\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Open an interactive SQLite shell connected to the internal g.db database
.PP
Launches `sqlite3` with the path to `~/.config/g/g.db` so you can run arbitrary SQL queries for debugging.  Pass `\-\-path` to print the database path without opening a shell.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-path\fR
Print the database path and exit (don\*(Aqt open the shell)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
